  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The main character is the popular streamer Evelone192, who has to save Buster and Lixxx!</strong></h2><br>This game is a story driven narrative where you have to fight, shoot, run away and all in order to save your friends!<br><br>Interesting and funny cut-scenes, several mini-games, nice graphics and original 3D models of popular streamers are waiting for you!<br><br>You will be able to:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fight with members of the \"Anti-Freak Squad\" in third-person with cool animations;<br></li><li>Shoot with a sniper rifle on the roof;<br></li><li>Sweep the rooms with a pistol in first-person.</li></ul>",
